        <num>CCP 4464</num>
        <heading>4464.  Court costs</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 4464.  Court costs
In proceedings under this Chapter, court costs shall be one-half of the court costs in similar proceedings in larger tutorships, provided that the minimum costs in any case shall be one hundred dollars.</p>
        </content>
